WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:06.166
Su Qingyu, that idiot.

2
00:00:06.166 --> 00:00:08.400
When mother and grandmother return...

3
00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:09.866
I'll make sure she pays.

4
00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:12.200
Hmm.

5
00:00:12.766 --> 00:00:14.666
Hahaha.

6
00:00:14.900 --> 00:00:16.700
How is it? Ugly enough?

7
00:00:16.700 --> 00:00:19.000
If you think it's not ugly enough, I can make it worse.

8
00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:21.200
Yesterday, I was just angry for a moment.

9
00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:23.566
You can't hold it against me, okay?

10
00:00:23.766 --> 00:00:24.833
Good that you understand.

11
00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:26.133
Hahaha, alright.

12
00:00:26.133 --> 00:00:27.433
Since you're so obedient,

13
00:00:27.666 --> 00:00:29.633
I won't tell mother about yesterday.

14
00:00:29.666 --> 00:00:31.500
Thank you, sister, for your generosity.

15
00:00:33.666 --> 00:00:36.433
Idiot, Lady Wang is here!

16
00:00:38.466 --> 00:00:39.266
Coming!

17
00:00:39.266 --> 00:00:41.766
Lady Wang from the Empress Dowager's side is notoriously strict.

18
00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:43.466
Did no one teach you?

19
00:00:43.466 --> 00:00:46.333
This makeup will probably be rejected in the first round.

20
00:00:46.333 --> 00:00:48.100
How long has the emperor been asleep?

21
00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:49.533
Have you called the imperial physician?

22
00:00:49.533 --> 00:00:50.466
Replying to the Empress Dowager,

23
00:00:51.133 --> 00:00:53.866
Imperial Physician Hu has already prepared a special calming incense for His Majesty.

24
00:00:53.966 --> 00:00:56.100
He says His Majesty will wake up soon.

25
00:01:04.266 --> 00:01:05.066
Empress.

26
00:01:06.133 --> 00:01:07.500
What happened to the emperor?

27
00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:09.200
Did something happen?

28
00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:11.266
What is going on?

29
00:01:11.333 --> 00:01:13.000
Isn't he dead?

30
00:01:14.733 --> 00:01:16.500
Mother, you're still here.

31
00:01:18.866 --> 00:01:19.666
Hmph.

32
00:01:20.166 --> 00:01:23.366
It seems the emperor is still angry about the selection.

33
00:01:23.466 --> 00:01:26.766
Now you're all grieving, and I don't dare say anything.

34
00:01:27.333 --> 00:01:30.500
Emperor, I think you've been charmed by Noble Consort Yan.

35
00:01:30.500 --> 00:01:33.500
Since ancient times, has any emperor ruled his harem for one person?

36
00:01:33.533 --> 00:01:35.533
Now, not only are you breaking ancestral rules for a woman...

37
00:01:35.533 --> 00:01:37.333
but you're even cursing me, the Empress Dowager.

38
00:01:37.333 --> 00:01:39.466
I haven't done anything wrong.

39
00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:42.066
Mother, what are you saying?

40
00:01:42.066 --> 00:01:43.500
Today is the selection day.

41
00:01:43.733 --> 00:01:46.866
Now the candidates have entered the palace, and you're still backing out?

42
00:01:46.866 --> 00:01:49.166
Be careful, or you'll drown in the ministers' spit.

43
00:01:49.166 --> 00:01:50.700
Quickly, get me dressed.

44
00:01:50.800 --> 00:01:52.200
We'll be late otherwise.